---
title: Japanese-Style Teriyaki Fillet Steak with Ginger-Soy Greens & Sesame Rice
description: This taste of Japanese-inspired fine dining takes the classic fillet steak above and beyond with a few flavourful twists. There’s
crunchy greens infused with a ginger-soy sauce and sesame-spiked rice. And on top? Sweet teriyaki sauce and garlic create a rich
elixir you’ll want to drizzle over everything. Itadakimasu!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/japanese-teriyaki-premium-fillet-steak-e4571461.jpg
